  <scopecontent id="aspace_288a7556b6c861805d8516c623bc8bac">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>This collection contains photographs and ephemera from the Kasper family of Brooklyn. These include photographs of the blizzard of 1947 and the Manhattan Beach Veterans Housing Project, as well as materials relating to Carol Kasper's dance classes and Irving Kasper's military service.</p>  </scopecontent>
